Class MultiContentHandler

java.lang.Object
org.odftoolkit.odfdom.pkg.rdfa.MultiContentHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContentHandler
public class MultiContentHandler extends Object implements ContentHandler
A proxy for delegating the parsing events to its sub ContentHandler(s).
